         <div type="translation">
            <ab>The place and the platform are (the property) of <seg cert="low">Bitos</seg>
               <supplied reason="lost">son of</supplied>
               <gap reason="lost" unit="character" extent="unknown"/>rotikos son of
Praulios, also known as Asterios, <term xml:lang="la">cursor</term>, of the most revered <term xml:lang="la">phylae</term>; if anyone should wish, without my
knowledge, to bury anyone in <supplied reason="subaudible">here</supplied>, he will give to the most sacred
treasury one pound of gold.</ab>
         </div>
